 1991-23541991-11-280,  EC,  ,  ,  , 
PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1989-988, which accepted from the Province of SASKATCHEWAN the transfer of certain lands, by deleting therefrom the words: "for so long as the said lands are administered, preserved and maintained by Her Majesty in right of Canada as National Historic Park" and substituting therefor the words: "for so long as the said lands are administered and maintained by Her Majesty in right of Canada for park purposes in support of the FORT WALSH NATIONAL HISTORIC PARK".
